qas.question: What happens at Broadway below 8th Street?
What happens at Fifth Avenue from 8th street and above?
Do streets' names change from West to East or North to South?

context: <a0_0><a1_0>Streets' names change<a1_0/><a0_0/> from <a2_0>West to East<a2_0/> (for instance, East 10th Street to West 10th Street) at Broadway below 8th Street, and at Fifth Avenue from 8th Street and above.
